   270	### `reference/compose/.env.example`
   271	
   272	Plain dotenv. Comments document each value. Ships dev-only secrets:
   273	
   274	```dotenv
   275	# EDEN reference Compose stack — example environment.
   276	# Copy to ".env" for local use; "compose up" reads from .env automatically.
   277	# CI uses these defaults verbatim; do NOT use these in production.
   278	
   279	# --- Postgres ---
   280	POSTGRES_DB=eden
   281	POSTGRES_USER=eden
   282	POSTGRES_PASSWORD=eden-dev-password-change-me
   283	POSTGRES_HOST_PORT=5433
   284	
   285	# --- Gitea ---
   286	# SECRET_KEY: gitea uses this for cookie / CSRF / 2FA encryption.
   287	# Generate with: gitea generate secret SECRET_KEY  (or 64 hex chars).
   288	GITEA_SECRET_KEY=0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcd
   289	# INTERNAL_TOKEN: gitea uses this for inter-component auth.
   290	GITEA_INTERNAL_TOKEN=0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef0123456789abcd
   291	GITEA_HOST_PORT=3001
   292	GITEA_SSH_HOST_PORT=2222
   293	```
